text: Cryoturris dominicensis is an extinct species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Mangeliidae.Fossilworks: Kurtziella (Cryoturris) dominicensis ==Description== ==Distribution== This extinct marine species has been found in strata of Cercado Formation of Santo Domingo. ==References== * * W. P. Woodring. 1970. Geology and paleontology of canal zone and adjoining parts of Panama: Description of Tertiary mollusks (gastropods: Eulimidae, Marginellidae to Helminthoglyptidae). United States Geological Survey Professional Paper 306(D): 299–452 ==External links== * dominicensis
title: Cryoturris dominicensis
